{"tid":560260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英防長宣布 3月派艦駛入南海","createTime":"2018-02-14T02:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T02:19:12.000Z","uid":56015,"like":93,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"4ef92f748853c74c0e9121a9e813e78a094e259a","tid":560260,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:46:08.000Z","msg":"2018/02/13 09:53<br />\n<br />\n（中央社雪梨13日綜合外電報導）英國國防大臣威廉森（Gavin Williamson）今天表示，英國一艘軍艦下月會由澳洲駛入爭議的南海水域，以主張自由航行權。此舉料將激怒北京。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，威廉森表示，反潛巡防艦蘇瑟蘭號（HMS Sutherland）本週稍晚就會抵達澳洲。<br />\n<br />\n威廉森在結束雪梨與坎培拉2天訪問行程後告訴「澳洲人報」（The Australian）：「蘇瑟蘭號（返國途中）會駛入南海，以清楚表明我們的海軍有權這樣做。」<br />\n<br />\n但威廉森不願說明英艦是否比照美國軍艦的作法，駛入中方所擁有島嶼或人造島的12海里內。<br />\n<br />\n在另一場接受澳洲廣播公司（ABC）的訪問裡，威廉森提醒各方，在中國大陸尋求成為全球性超級強權時，有警惕中方「各種惡意企圖」的必要。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「澳洲與英國視中國為一個有偉大機會的國家，但我們不應對中國的野心視若無睹，我們要捍衛自身的國家安全利益。」（譯者：陳亦偉/核稿：蔡佳敏）1070213<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201802130028-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201802130028-1.aspx&d=nZ3leCUZjns4JbAcFq8YcL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=34fede41\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201802130028-1.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"c5ab05a01bd57f304b6b6c860b4dc4be03b8bcdf","tid":560260,"uid":20522,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:46:59.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec40fc09efc7e458b6ecbc637b74a47b8b51020","tid":560260,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:47:14.000Z","msg":"中國外交部：當前南海風平浪靜　有關方面不要無風起浪 <br />\n<br />\n2018-02-13 HKT 16:11<br />\n<br />\n耿爽說，希望有關方面，特別是域外國家，尊重地區國家的努力，不要無風起浪。（仇志榮攝）<br />\n<br />\n有報道引述英國國防大臣韋廉信指，英國一艘戰艦下月將從澳洲啟航，經南海返回英國。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人耿爽說，各國依據國際法在南海享有航行和飛越自由，對此各方沒有分歧。他說，在中國和南海沿岸國共同努力下，南海航行和飛越自由均不存在任何問題，南海局勢也正日益向好的方向發展。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽說，希望有關方面，特別是域外國家，尊重地區國家的努力，當前南海風平浪靜，有關方面不要無風起浪。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1380731-20180213.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1380731-20180213.htm&d=nZ3leCUZjns4JbAcFq8YcL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=9184987f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1380731-20180213.htm&h=b5aaa23e\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1380731-20180213.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1b0944dd3d87ea7d1813caf9e9b27af3138cb1e7","tid":560260,"uid":57844,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:48:22.000Z","msg":"洗牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洗牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127cdc9068cd927f9b9e05b6c7680cce9171846a","tid":560260,"uid":20522,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:51:46.000Z","msg":"美英法澳日韓越南菲律賓圍毆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04393fbbf3a8e1ef0f8d1b91461e3dfcfa437c8d","tid":560260,"uid":38671,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:53:00.000Z","msg":"全部埋位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b64d5c0f5511259d64b6cc0461f14a5c6ee59a","tid":560260,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5c3beab2f3cf4d00ceba8dc3b4df24e611c695","tid":560260,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:54:35.000Z","msg":"我係大陸就開槍還擊算數"},{"pid":"5e4f798079ac5df64298e470a5389041119cfff0","tid":560260,"uid":56015,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:57:38.000Z","msg":"[同場加影] 蔡英文:台灣國防預算將會年年增加<br />\n<br />\n13-02-2018<br />\n<br />\n據中央社報道，蔡英文表示，面對軍事威脅，國軍要時時保持警戒，和平不是平白得來，需有堅強的國防做後盾；中華民國是愛好和<br />\n平的國家，我們不求戰，也不畏戰，未來國防預算會年年增加。她說：&ldquo;國家安全要拜託你們了&rdquo;。<br />\n蔡英文的勞軍活動包括，聽取部隊簡報，視導防空部隊戰備演練，與官兵在檞樹飛彈車前合影，與官兵會餐，席間頒發加菜金。<br />\n據法廣駐台北特約記者陳民峰13日報道，台灣空軍已透過管道，與美方討論出售F-15與F-18戰機的可能性。未來台灣將用這些美式戰<br />\n機取代法國的幻象戰機，執行高空高速攔截任務。<br />\n另據中央社今天引述總部設在倫敦的國際戰略研究所專家指出，中國軍力開始挑戰美國。中國逐漸取代俄羅斯，成為美國制訂武裝力<br />\n量標準的指標，特別是在中國追求現代化的空軍和海軍方面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0/20180213-%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%83%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%B4%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0%2F20180213-%25E8%2594%25A1%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2598%25B2%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%258A%25A0&d=nZ3leCUZjns4JbAcFq8YcL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=2248a132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0/20180213-%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%9C%8B%E9%98%B2%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%83%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%B4%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0</a>"},{"pid":"137c041cb704ad24e621d99a5801c3671e3179bb","tid":560260,"uid":65346,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:57:51.000Z","msg":"我要維港&quot;燒&quot;鴉片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965e2423ed6e8b3bc6bd83c520af5b486f4673e9","tid":560260,"uid":162424,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T02:58:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"447920e7f55ecf83992aef7fe98465e23b905a3c","tid":560260,"uid":14918,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T03:03:32.000Z","msg":"支持軍委主席習大大打響第一槍"},{"pid":"e186bdb22d3954cbd018f99e1ffe67e8d775793b","tid":560260,"uid":37539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-1